book.title: Deadtown (Deadtown #1)
book.description: Storyline: Deadtown (Deadtown #1) If you were undead, you'd be home by now... They call it Deadtown: the city's quarantined section for its inhuman and undead residents. Most humans stay far from its borders-but Victory Vaughn, Boston's only professional demon slayer, isn't exactly human.
book.author: Nancy Holzner
